ingredients.ingredient: 1 (7.5 ounce) package refrigerated buttermilk biscuit dough
3 ounces mozzarella cheese, cut into 3/4 inch cubes

cookingTips: Ensure mozzarella cubes are cold to prevent excessive melting during baking
Don't overstuff the biscuits or cheese will leak out during cooking
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Walk me through how to wrap biscuit dough around cheese cubes to create a sealed puff without leaking.
